	   <tr><td colspan=2>First, I will agree that this item can be used by every class for one reason or another.&nbsp;&nbsp;As an enchanter the item provides several things that would be beneficial.  The INT is a given, all pure casters can use it.  The CHA is also a plus for helping with mezzes, etc.  The additional mana is something again, that any type of caster, priest, hybrid, or pure caster, would use.  The strength would be a plus for an enchanter to help carry items, but not really a requirement.  The agility helps keep from getting hit.  An enchanter not getting hit is more apt to get a mez so to me, this item has more stats that benefit the enchanter class directly, based on primary stats than any other class; however, I still believe that this item makes one of the best back items for anyone who can obtain it.<br>&nbsp;<br></td></tr>
